They trusted his routine .
He would always wear his hat .
He would always go to El Guayabo , the bar across from the office , and always sit there at the same table .
Now they ask : was his love of routine his ruin ?
His death has also forced them to question their own assumptions about how best to do their job and stay alive .
" You don 't like it when you 're dealing with their wives , their children , their clean shops , their secret runways " to move drugs .
