The user can also " customize " his robot according to his beliefs , choosing everything from the robot 's eye color , the shape of the nipples , to the type or color of his fingernails .
But it becomes even more troubling , as many robots possess the " personalities " that would make a Stepford woman look progressive .
Modern sex dolls have evolved into robots with a silicone skin .
