On the other hand , in a department store this week , I was forced to rate my " experience " of transactions on a scale of one to five stars before I could go through my credit card .
At the coffee shop on the corner of my street , it 's the same , plus the option to match the rating with a 15 percent tip - this to buy something over the counter .
